name: Blood elf song
description:
Dark fog in the valley of memory,
where the shadows of the past days
forever roam, do not disappear, do not die
where the stars far flicker
where we sleep white flowers
In the dark waters of the lake
and blue herbs in the lunar rays,
Everything covers a dark fog.
Sleep, and let the IRMO send you a dream
What will come tomorrow.
Let the bright light of the sun
Shines in dew on green sheets
Let the shadows of the previous years leave forever
Let me, irmo, sleep
About the beginning of a new life.
